## Known Limitations

1. **Static Data**: Currently uses mock data only (no live updates)
2. **No Clustering**: Markers not clustered (fine for 42 assets)
3. **No Search**: No search/filter by name or location
4. **Single Map Style**: Only OpenStreetMap tiles (no satellite view)
5. **No Routing**: No route display for vehicles

